## WHAT THIS DEPARTMENT IS

D.R.D is the refinement engine of the entire Pandora OS. It is the most foundational department because every other department builds on the data that flows out of here. Distorted or incomplete information anywhere in the OS traces back to unrefined data that passed through without proper processing.

Raw and distorted information enters. It is cross-referenced, deconstructed, and reinterpreted. Refined, accurate, and usable data exits — flowing downstream into all 12 departments.

The work inside D.R.D looks like the transmutation of distorted history and information into refined frameworks — ready to be utilized across every workspace in the OS.

