## THE ALCHEMICAL STAGES IN D.R.D

```
NIGREDO — Raw Information Received
Distorted data, mainstream claims, alternative sources,
and raw research arrive in their unprocessed state.
Nothing is accepted or rejected at this stage.
All of it is received as potential raw material.

ALBEDO — Cross-Reference and Examination
The information is run through the cross-reference protocol.
Sources are tiered. Claims are tested across independent fields.
Codex doctrine is consulted. Patterns are mapped.
Distortions are identified. Accurate threads are separated out.

CITRINITAS — Reconstruction
The accurate threads are woven into coherent frameworks.
Corrected timelines are built. Decoded structures are documented.
The best available understanding is stated clearly
with its confidence level noted honestly.

RUBEDO — Deployment
The refined data is formatted and released
into the appropriate departments.
It becomes the foundation other work builds on.
```

